    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently non-operational. It requires a total powertrain rebuild, as both the engine and transmission have failed, and the electrical system shows intermittent faults. The exterior has heavy rust on the rocker panels, several deep dents, and the clear coat is peeling significantly across the roof and trunk. This is strictly a project car or a parts donor for someone with the tools and time for a complete overhaul.",
