    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary choice for the discerning driver who values both performance and mechanical integrity. This specimen has been meticulously maintained, presenting a sophisticated aesthetic and a robust driving experience that exceeds standard expectations. Rigorously inspected to ensure long-term reliability, it offers a refined cabin environment and consistent operational excellence. This vehicle represents a premier acquisition for those seeking a high-caliber automotive investment that balances prestige with proven durability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
