      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? I'm parting with my car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, clean, and runs like a dream. It has a few minor signs of love from its time on the road, but overall, it's a fantastic vehicle that's ready for its next adventure. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 power plant. This unit boasts a linear power delivery via its six individual throttle bodies and precise Double VANOS actuation. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventive measure for this platform. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power to a limited-slip differential that remains tight. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain the signature telepathic handling. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain and structural integrity are dialed in for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Reliable performance. Clean title. Well-maintained interior and exterior.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle offers an exceptional balance of performance and daily utility, presenting in a state that reflects consistent, careful ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous metallic finish; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway use, the body panels are straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment. The leather upholstery is supple and clean, showing only light softening on the driver-side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All interior electronics\u2014including the high-fidelity audio system, navigation, and heated seating\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has followed a strict synthetic oil change schedule, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. Recent service includes a fresh brake fluid flush and a cooling system inspection. The vehicle sits on well-maintained alloy wheels wrapped in tires with substantial tread depth remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free car that drives with the tightness and composure you would expect from a well-loved machine. It comes complete with two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of service receipts.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and long-term reliability. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning buyer. We invite you to inspect this exceptional value proposition, which represents a premier balance of performance and prestige.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved? I'm parting with my car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been such a dependable companion for me. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the regular maintenance, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Come by, take it for a test drive, and see for yourself how great it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering tactile engagement and precise gear selection. Crucial preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension utilizes Bilstein dampers for improved rebound characteristics, while the M-Variable limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. Though it displays minor cosmetic patina reflective of its driver-status, the powertrain remains robust with documented rod bearing service. This is a turnkey performance machine engineered for the purist who values throttle response and chassis feedback.",
      "price": 31500.0,
